because you somehow

16:24.849 --> 16:26.338
don't get around
to doing it before I...

16:26.405 --> 16:28.821
Oh, my God.
Is that your car?

16:30.250 --> 16:32.626
Yeah. I just got it.

16:34.497 --> 16:36.563
