21:16.449 --> 21:17.559
Drink.

21:26.324 --> 21:28.434
I'm gonna open
another bottle.

21:30.493 --> 21:32.285
Where are you from, Vik?

21:32.563 --> 21:33.980
I'm from here.

21:34.383 --> 21:36.161
My dad's from Lebanon,

21:36.228 --> 21:38.434
and my mom's from Mumbai.

21:40.172 --> 21:41.738
Do they know?

21:43.500 --> 21:44.881
I'm not sure.

21:44.948 --> 21:46.262
What do you mean?

21:46.524 --> 21:47.826
I told them,

21:47.893 --> 21:49.180
but...

21:51.086 --> 21:53.246
they won't hear that I'm sick.

21:54.670 --> 21:56.488
Like, literally.

21:57.211 --> 21:59.488
