22:00.118 --> 22:01.617
And today, I heard myself

22:01.684 --> 22:04.543
promising them that Helen
was going to have my baby.

22:05.899 --> 22:07.141
Really?

22:07.568 --> 22:08.817
For them.

22:09.407 --> 22:10.637
Not for me.

22:11.416 --> 22:13.113
Not for her.

22:14.266 --> 22:15.758
For them.

22:16.946 --> 22:19.855
So I don't fail them completely.

22:28.398 --> 22:29.816
You know, I think...

22:33.118 --> 22:37.137
I think, when you have
immigrant parents,

22:37.449 --> 22:39.910
you end up being
responsible for them.

22:40.907 --> 22:42.668
Like, you're the parent.

22:44.281 --> 22:46.113
Yeah, I know that feeling.

22:47.368 --> 22:50.051
I was the perfect immigrant son.

22:51.118 --> 22:53.301
But I made a deal with myself...

22:53.535 --> 22:55.051
long time ago.

22:56.930 --> 23:00.147
I said, okay,
I will become a doctor

23:00.214 --> 23:02.707
because that's what they want.

23:03.282 --> 23:05.551
And I will support them,

23:05.854 --> 23:08.191
and I will make them proud.

23:09.086 --> 23:10.501
I'll even move back to L.A.

23:10.568 --> 23:12.482
