a part of me that...

23:38.807 --> 23:41.012
liked that, you know?

23:42.055 --> 23:46.098
Because I knew it was gonna
drive them fucking crazy.

23:50.234 --> 23:51.855
Everything...

23:55.483 --> 23:57.895
Everything I've done

23:59.149 --> 24:01.441
has either been for

24:02.191 --> 24:04.671
or in reaction to them.

24:08.235 --> 24:10.598
I'm 45 years old.

24:12.734 --> 24:15.715
I'm at the top of my profession.

24:17.865 --> 24:19.668
I'm going to die.

24:23.106 --> 24:27.895
And I haven't really made
a single choice for myself.

25:06.149 --> 25:09.324
Guess what my mother's
favorite thing about me is.

25:11.657 --> 25:12.930
What?

25:13.391 --> 25:14.782
My skin.

25:17.866 --> 25:18.866
Your skin?

25:18.969 --> 25:20.668
Yeah, my skin.

25:21.149 --> 25:23.027
She's obsessed with it.

25:23.423 --> 25:25.317
Whenever I see her,
she's always

25:25.839 --> 25:27.668
touching it
or pinching it.

25:32.519 --> 25:35.918
She will never forgive me
for being younger than she is.

29:17.664 --> 29:18.852
Hey.

29:19.417 --> 29:20.542
Help you?

29:20.610 --> 29:21.757
Yeah, maybe.

29:21.824 --> 29:23.941
I mean, it's probably
a lost cause,

29:24.008 --> 29:25.826
