31:29.800 --> 31:30.941
Gabriel.

31:31.009 --> 31:32.301
Excuse me?

31:35.545 --> 31:37.992
I'm... I'm so sorry.

31:38.059 --> 31:39.600
You just...

31:39.791 --> 31:42.856
You just look so much
like someone I used to know.

31:42.923 --> 31:44.585
Gabriel Lockhart.

31:44.847 --> 31:45.847
Yes.

31:46.792 --> 31:48.082
I'm sorry. I...

31:48.149 --> 31:49.632
I'm his son.

31:50.489 --> 31:52.095
My name is Cole.

31:54.240 --> 31:55.659
Well...

31:56.157 --> 31:58.151
this is unexpected.

31:58.218 --> 32:00.718
Nice to meet you, Cole.

32:00.878 --> 32:02.319
Uh, I'm Nan.

32:03.214 --> 32:05.780
- Is this your gallery?
- It is.

32:05.907 --> 32:07.463
Maybe you can help me
with something.

32:07.530 --> 32:08.820
This is my father's board,

32:08.887 --> 32:11.382
and it has the same
symbol on it.

32:11.753 --> 32:13.470
Oh, my God.

32:15.741 --> 32:17.120
May I?

32:17.597 --> 32:18.886
Sure.

32:21.074 --> 32:22.803
Look at this.

32:24.449 --> 32:25.947
Does it still float?

32:26.014 --> 32:27.034
