32:28.313 --> 32:30.238
I had no idea
what I was doing.

32:30.305 --> 32:32.340
I was so young.

32:32.407 --> 32:34.095
You made this board?

32:35.434 --> 32:36.895
I did.

32:37.597 --> 32:38.984
You're a shaper?

32:39.051 --> 32:40.422
Not exactly.

32:40.489 --> 32:43.367
